archimate:BusinessObject.name: Sovrin Ledger Fee
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation: The fee in fiat currency, Sovrin Tokens, or other units of economic value for making a write to the Sovrin Ledger. See Sovrin Governing Bodies for more information about the process of governing Sovrin Ledger Fees.
